<i>noun</i>: 혈안 [혀란], 필사 [필싸], 자포자기 [자포자기] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>혈안 [혀란]</dt><br>
<dd>1. bloodshot eyes</dd><br>
<dd>피가 비정상적으로 많이 모여 붉게 된 눈.</dd><br>
<dd>Eyes that have turned red due to an abnormal concentration of blood.</dd><br>
<dd>2. desperation</dd><br>
<dd>기를 쓰고 달려들어 독이 오른 눈.</dd><br>
<dd>The eyes that show the person's intensity and will to achieve his/her aim.</dd><br>
<dt>필사 [필싸]</dt><br>
<dd>desperation; franticness</dd><br>
<dd>죽기를 각오하고 힘을 다함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being determined to risk one's life, doing something with all one's might.</dd><br>
<dt>자포자기 [자포자기]</dt><br>
<dd>giving oneself up; desperation; self-abandonment</dd><br>
<dd>절망에 빠져서 스스로 자신을 돌보지 않고 모든 일을 포기함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of giving up everything and not taking care of oneself in despair.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>